142
00:09:33,218 --> 00:09:35,053
<i>Kami butuh bantuan kalian.</i>

143
00:09:37,388 --> 00:09:38,264
<i>Tolong</i>

144
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:41,434
<i>suarakan pendapat kalian dan dukung kami</i>

145
