00:55:54,419 --> 00:55:57,923
Apa yang dilakukan Menteri Kehakiman
sekarang?

853
00:55:58,423 --> 00:56:00,884
JOOJIN CHEMICAL

854
00:56:00,967 --> 00:56:03,470
MENTERI SONG HUI-SEOP

855
00:56:05,722 --> 00:56:06,973
Ya, Menteri Song.

